      <div>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.8rem;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:1rem;">We Help Indian Food Businesses Make Smarter Equipment Decisions</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;">BakeDesk Equipment was built out of frustration. When we talked to bakery owners and restaurant operators across India, we kept hearing the same problem: equipment buying is a nightmare.</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;">Suppliers quote wildly different prices. Online information is either too vague or written for Western markets. And once you've bought the wrong machine, you're stuck with it.</p>
        <p>So we built BakeDesk — India's most detailed, honest, and India-specific guide to commercial bakery and restaurant equipment. Every price we list comes from real Indian suppliers. Every comparison is based on actual use cases in Indian kitchens.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--navy),var(--navy-dark));border-radius:16px;padding:2.5rem;color:#fff;text-align:center;">
