        <h3>Pan-India Coverage</h3>
        <p>We have supplier relationships in Delhi, Mumbai, Bangalore, Chennai, Hyderabad, and over 50 other cities across India.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.8rem;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:1rem;">Who We Help</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;">BakeDesk serves a wide range of food businesses across India:</p>
    <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;margin-bottom:2rem;line-height:2;">
      <li><strong>Home bakers scaling up</strong> — transitioning from home to commercial production</li>
      <li><strong>New bakery owners</strong> — setting up their first commercial bakery kitchen</li>
      <li><strong>Restaurant operators</strong> — equipping full-service restaurants and QSRs</li>
      <li><strong>Cloud kitchen entrepreneurs</strong> — building efficient, compact commercial kitchens</li>
      <li><strong>Cafe owners</strong> — outfitting cafes with the right baking and coffee equipment</li>
      <li><strong>Hotel chains</strong> — large-scale procurement of bakery and kitchen equipment</li>
      <li><strong>Catering businesses</strong> — equipping large-scale food production facilities</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.8rem;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:1rem;">Our Approach to Equipment Advice</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;">We don't take money from equipment manufacturers to recommend their products. Our guides are written based on real-world research, conversations with equipment users, and our own technical analysis.</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;">When we say a deck oven is better than a convection oven for artisan bread, it's because bakers told us so — not because a deck oven company paid us. When we list prices, they're from actual supplier quotations, not manufacturer suggested retail prices.</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom:2rem;">This independence is what makes BakeDesk useful. You'll find honest comparisons like <a href="/blog/deck-oven-vs-convection-oven">Deck Oven vs Convection Oven</a>, real breakdowns like <a href="/blog/bakery-setup-cost-india">Bakery Setup Cost in India</a>, and practical guides like <a href="/blog/how-to-buy-bakery-equipment">How to Buy Bakery Equipment</a>.</p>

