        <a href="tel:+918826431351" class="btn-call-sm">Call +91-8826431351</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.8rem;color:var(--navy);margin:2rem 0 1rem;">Based in Delhi. Serving All of India.</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom:1rem;">BakeDesk is headquartered in Delhi, giving us direct access to one of India's largest equipment trading hubs. But we serve food businesses across the country — from Srinagar to Kanyakumari, Dwarka to Dibrugarh.</p>
    <p>Our supplier network spans all major cities and we regularly work with businesses in Tier 2 and Tier 3 towns where local equipment expertise can be hard to find.</p>

